summary: An ordinance relating to zoning, establishing Use, Area, and Height Districts for all of Lake Ridge Division No. 3 and No. 4, and that portion of the northeast one-quarter of the northeast one-quarter of Section 11, Township 23 North, Range 4 East, W. M., lying east of east line of Renton Avenue, annexed to the City of Seattle under Ordinance No. 45382, as amended, by adding thereto three new sections numbered 2-161, 10-7, 17-117, respectively.
